title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update IX Italy & Malta - released
description:
It has been just released World Update IX which has the focus on Italy and Malta.
Next week the next World Update for MSFS will be released, to be exact on the 17th of May. In addition to this Local Hero IV will be made available which is a paid add-on being available via the marketplace. In this video we will look at some screenshots already released and discuss about what to expect in the World Update including some guessing because not all details have been released yet.
